# Brand orange

When the user says "orange" or when choosing accent / brand orange colors:

| Role | Hex | CSS variable |
|------|-----|--------------|
| Primary orange | `#f6672a` | `--color-accent` |
| Deep orange (hover, shadows, secondary) | `#f54900` | `--color-accent-deep`, `--color-accent-muted` |

- Prefer `var(--color-accent)` and `var(--color-accent-deep)` over Tailwind `orange-*` utilities or other hex values.
- Do not use legacy oranges (`#f58220`, `#e85d04`, `#ff9a4d`, `orange-500`, etc.).
